<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-23-1177 </DOCNO><TEXT>Because it is nearly impossible with todays technology to make a processorwhich is optimized for all possible image processing tasks one triesto realize different processors each of them being a compromise betweentechnology, processing speed and class of operations that must be performedoptimaly. For the authors' Image Computer a new processor, called theTransformation Process, is optimized for a specific class of operations.</TEXT></DOC>